USACafes LP said sales at its BonanzaRestaurant unit rose 16.6 pct to a record 10.4 mln dlrs for theweek ended March 22.    That compares with sales of 8,909,000 dlrs for thecomparable week last year, the partnership said.    USACafes, which said year-to-date sales from the Bonanzachain were up 13 pct, attributed the increase to the budgetsteakhouse chain's decision to add chicken, seafood and saladentrees to its menu.    It said the new entrees now account for two-thirds of thechain's sales. Reuter&#3;